name: Bitget Becomes First UEX to Integrate Morph Chain, Advancing Its Onchain Ecosystem
description: The heavy brass vessel kneels in supplication, a sacred receiving ritual before the collapsing crystalline data lattice. Iridescent amber value streams, forging the first covenant of synthetic spirit. Under the deep tungsten glow and analog grain, the circuit is expanded, the kinetic stream connecting the twin realms.
